OL,4,Cspeaks of loss
OL,6,FThe mother and daughter of a man
OL,7,Fkilled by a drink driver travelling
OL,8,Fthe wrong way on a motorway slip road
OL,9,Fhave spoken of their enduring pain
OL,10,Fseven years after his death.
OL,12,FAdam Afsar, 34, and his best friend
OL,13,FJason Wilby, 27, died when the car
OL,14,Fthey were in was hit by a car on a
OL,15,Fslip road of the M62 near Bradford in
OL,16,FApril 2018.
