OL,4,Cspeaks of loss
OL,6,FThe driver of the other vehicle, 23-
OL,7,Fyear-old Taryl Moxam, was twice the
OL,8,Fdrink drive limit and had taken
OL,9,Fcocaine following a night out. He was
OL,10,Fjailed for more than nine years.
OL,12,FSpeaking as West Yorkshire Police
OL,13,Flaunched its annual drink driving
OL,14,Fcampaign, Mr Afsar's mother Christine
OL,15,FPeace said: "I cry every day, every
OL,16,Fsingle day.
OL,18,F"I come in the kitchen cooking and a
OL,19,Fmemory will come and I'll just hit the
OL,20,Ffloor and it's just overwhelming when
OL,21,Fthat happens."
