OL,6,FShe added: "But that's my normal.
OL,7,FThat's my life now. There's no finish
OL,8,Fline for us, this is it now."
OL,10,FMr Asfar's 15-year-old daughter,
OL,11,FMiley, said she still suffered.
OL,13,F"It's made me very unsociable," she
OL,14,Fsaid. "All I want to do is just be in
OL,15,Fmy own space and be with my mum. And
OL,16,Fit's affected me a lot later in life
OL,17,Fbecause I was seven years old, so I
OL,18,Fdidn't understand.
