OL,6,F"So it's affecting me as I've gone
OL,7,Finto high school really, because
OL,8,Fthat's when I've started to understand
OL,9,Fit."
OL,11,FThroughout December, West Yorkshire
OL,12,FPolice will carry out extra patrols
OL,13,Freminding people of the potentially
OL,14,Ffatal consequences of driving while
OL,15,Funder the influence.
OL,17,FCh Insp James Farrar, head of our the
OL,18,Froads policing unit said: "Each year
OL,19,Fwe hear the same excuses: 'I only had
OL,20,Fa couple', 'I wasn't going far', 'I
OL,21,Fhaven't had a drink since last night'.
