OL,6,F"Ultimately there can never be any
OL,7,Fjustification for getting behind the
OL,8,Fwheel under the influence of drink or
OL,9,Fdrugs.
OL,11,F"The consequences can include a fine,
OL,12,Fa driving ban or a prison sentence.
OL,13,FMost importantly, you might have to
OL,14,Flive with the knowledge that you have
OL,15,Fseriously injured or killed an
OL,16,Finnocent person due to the choices you
OL,17,Fmade.
