OL,3,CDaughter of man killed by drink driver
OL,4,Cspeaks of loss
OL,6,F"The lasting impact on Adam's family
OL,7,Fis truly heart-breaking to see, and I
OL,8,Fwould like to thank them for
OL,9,Fsupporting our campaign in the hope it
OL,10,Fmight make somebody else think twice."
OL,12,FChristine said: "One pint can do it.
OL,13,FJust phone somebody. Phone somebody to
OL,14,Fpick you up, don't get, leave your car
OL,15,Fat home."
